INSERT INTO service_faqs (service_page_id, question, answer, faq_order) VALUES
  (867, 'What data and network infrastructure does a Pacific Palisades commercial building need?', 'Modern Pacific Palisades commercial properties—whether hospitality venues, medical offices, or corporate headquarters—require robust data infrastructure to support operations, guest services, and business continuity. Shaffer Construction designs and installs enterprise-grade cabling systems that support high-speed internet, secure networks, surveillance systems, and intelligent building controls. We assess your specific needs and build scalable infrastructure that grows with your Pacific Palisades business.', 1),
  (867, 'How can professional AV systems improve client experience at my Pacific Palisades business?', 'Professional audio-visual systems create memorable experiences for clients and guests visiting your Pacific Palisades location. High-quality conference room systems facilitate productive meetings and remote collaboration. Integrated digital signage communicates with customers throughout your space. Shaffer Construction designs and installs these systems seamlessly, ensuring crystal-clear video, distortion-free audio, and intuitive controls that impress both clients and employees at your Pacific Palisades property.', 2),
  (867, 'What is fiber optic cabling and why might my Pacific Palisades business need it?', 'Fiber optic cabling transmits data at the speed of light, providing ultra-high-speed, interference-free connections ideal for Pacific Palisades businesses with demanding bandwidth requirements. Properties with multiple buildings, extensive video conferencing, large file transfers, or HD surveillance benefit significantly from fiber backbone infrastructure. Shaffer Construction evaluates your data demands and recommends whether fiber connectivity makes sense for your specific operations, then expertly installs and tests the system.', 3),
  (867, 'Can you integrate new AV systems with existing infrastructure at my Pacific Palisades location?', 'Absolutely. Many Pacific Palisades properties have existing network and electrical systems. Shaffer Construction evaluates your current infrastructure, identifies integration points, and seamlessly adds new AV capabilities without disruptive overhauls. We coordinate the design and installation to minimize business interruption while delivering professional results that enhance your space and capabilities. Our expertise ensures new and existing systems work together reliably.', 4),
  (867, 'Why should I hire a licensed electrician for network and AV wiring in Pacific Palisades?', 'Professional installation ensures your systems meet Los Angeles electrical codes, perform reliably under business conditions, and function optimally for years. Shaffer Construction uses quality materials, proper installation techniques, comprehensive testing, and full documentation. We provide warranty coverage, ongoing support, and the expertise to troubleshoot issues quickly. For Pacific Palisades businesses, this professional approach protects your investment and ensures uninterrupted operations when you need it most.', 5);
